OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC Russian journalist     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbranded 'foreign agent'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Russian justice ministry has       
OL,6, labelled two prominent journalists -   
OL,7, BBC Russian correspondent Ilya         
OL,8, Barabanov and science reporter Asya    
OL,9, Kazantseva - as "foreign agents".      
OL,11,FBarabanov has written extensively about
OL,12,FRussia's war in Ukraine and the Wagner 
OL,13,Fmercenary group. The BBC condemned the 
OL,14,Fministry's move against him.           
OL,16,F"The BBC strongly rejects the          
OL,17,Fdecision," a BBC statement said.       
OL,19,FThe "foreign agent" label has very     
OL,20,Fnegative connotations in Russia.       
